{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"067f50c9cd","title":"关于欢迎李宗仁回国的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6aaab9672e","index":0,"year":1965,"month":2,"day":3,"articleId":"067f50c9cd"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[{"id":"1a42bf29d9","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李宗仁，原为国民党桂系首领。1948年4月任国民党政府副总统，1949年1月蒋介石引退后任国民党政府代总统。国民党政权崩溃后去美国。"},{"id":"0de2c4126e","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央调查部1965年1月31日印发的关于廖行健（李宗仁的桂林同乡）在香港谈李宗仁动态给毛泽东等的报告上。报告说，程思远（曾任国民党中央非常委员会副秘书长）1月25日报告，厦行健在香港对他说，李宗仁准备从美国经香港回到祖国。李为表示离美决心，已登广告出卖其新泽西州的房子，预定四五月间赴欧洲。他对去年在纽约《先驱前锋论坛报》投函事，非常追悔，惜已补救无及。现在回国是李唯一可行之路。可否先指示方针，季有所遵循。"},{"id":"3d8dd058a3","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"总理，指周恩来。14]柯西金，当时任苏联部长会议主席，1965年2月10日率领苏联代表团到达北京。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3dc2cf7901","type":"title","text":"关于欢迎李宗仁\"回国的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd"},{"id":"1a42bf29d9","type":"subtitle","text":"总理","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd"},{"id":"0de2c4126e","type":"paragraph","text":"似应欢迎季宗仁回国。去年向美报投书问题，无关大局，不加批评，因他已自己认错了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd"},{"id":"3d8dd058a3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd"},{"id":"ff762698c4","type":"paragraph","text":"二月三日上午","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd"},{"id":"6d3e1d5cfb","type":"paragraph","text":"柯西金何时到京，盼告。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd"}],"page":{"id":"9a2eb0d627","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"067f50c9cd","start":479,"end":479}}}},"__N_SSG":true}